    1.8  “Necessary Claims” means all patent claims owned or controlled by
         the Owner that are necessarily infringed by practicing the
         Software.

    1.9  “Commercial Distribution License” (“CDL”) means a separate written
         agreement, executed by the Owner and You, that expressly grants You
