          violations of §4.2 (patent retaliation), or to intentional
          infringement of the Owner’s intellectual-property rights, all of
          which result in immediate termination without notice.

    12.3  Post-Termination Obligations.  Upon termination, You must
          immediately cease all use of the Software and Derivative Works,
          destroy all copies in Your possession or control, and certify such
          destruction to the Owner in writing within fifteen (15) days.

    12.4  Survival.  §§3–6, 7.1–7.2, 8–15, and any other provision that by
          its nature should survive, shall survive termination.

